Class Jukebox

  • java.lang.Object
    • queues.Jukebox

  • public class Jukebox
extends java.lang.Object
    the class Jukebox to manage three objects of type Queue. The constructor reads the file with user's request for what song to add to which playlist. Created by Fu on 4/2/2018.
